<paragraph blockId="3.[1435,2665,2417,3474]" pageId="3" pageNumber="324">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1459,2172,3126,3159]" pageId="3" pageNumber="324">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
